org.berkholz.pamooba.config

Class MainConfiguration

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.berkholz.pamooba.config.MainConfiguration

  • public class MainConfiguration
extends Object
    Main configuration definition for the xml configuration file. It contains the database connection and select settings as variables from other classes.
    Author:
    Marcel Berkholz
